# RAG Project using Endee

## 📌 Overview
This project demonstrates a simple Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) system using Endee as a vector database.

## ⚙️ System Design
- Documents are converted into embeddings
- Query is embedded
- Similar documents are retrieved
- Response is generated based on retrieved data

## 🧠 Use of Endee
Endee is used as the vector database to store and retrieve embeddings efficiently.

## 🚀 Setup Instructions

1. Clone repo:
git clone https://github.com/your-username/endee.git

2. Install dependencies:
pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Run:
python app.py

## 💡 Features
- Semantic Search
- Simple RAG pipeline
- Fast retrieval
